- damage level 2
- timer 99",Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,There is a glitch where both players may be transported out of bounds and may be unable to move normally.  The round should continue and the players should forward dash to get out of this state.  If a player pauses during this glitch it may not count against them as this is not common knowledge.,"3/5 Games for Losers Finals, 3/5 Games for Winners Finals, 3/5 Games for Grand Finals","Brook Wingman Converters will be provided rather than requiring players bring their own. Converters are put in force digital mode (LED on the new model converter should be blue). This is more strictly enforced if a persons controller is capable of an uncleaned socd whether pure dpad or dpad + analog stick.
Instant super buttons are banned. Converter remap function is allowed, turbo not. (Please reset the converter bindings to default when you hop off if you use this function)

Pause penalty: round loss. Enforced as player eating penalty has to afk for the rest of the round

Games will be played in Arcade mode not Versus mode, for convenience.
players RPS/coin toss for choice of side.  After game 1, loser can change character and stage (winner must keep character)",2 Hours,"Thurs. 1/23, Fri. 1/24, Sat. 1/25, Sun. 1/26",,,6,,,,,,,6 / 32,,For setup purposes it would be ideal to run FUC after Soul Calibur 2 so they should be scheduled the same day,$200 personal contribution,200,recI66XSPyo4nQ7Cm,,,,
