- Custom characters and custom outfits are banned.
- All stage selections are random.
- Loser may roll a new random stage without changing character.
- TiZ's Stupid Rule: If the result is the same stage they were just on, they can reroll until they get a new one ONLY IF the opponent agrees. The opponent is under no obligation to agree and can rescind agreement at any time.",Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,,"3/5 Games for Losers Finals, 3/5 Games for Winners Finals, 3/5 Games for Grand Finals",,6 Hours,Fri. 1/24,Afternoon or early evening,,21,"Thurs. 1/23, Sun. 1/26",True,,recm0ZmhtzqQtZ7v1,,TiZ,21 / 64,,"Probably won't need this, but I am reserving a right to use Steam Decks as tournament setups if somehow we don't get enough PS4s. No Windows PCs!! They are terrible with controllers. Players may choose to skip playing on a Deck. Again, we probably will have enough PS4s, but I'm keeping this base covered.",,,,,,,
